  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil in a kadhai over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook until it's translucent, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the shrimp and cook until pink and fully cooked, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the Thai red curry paste and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the fish sauce, soy sauce, brown sugar, and palm sugar, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the coconut milk and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and add the tamarind paste, stirring to combine.",
    "Cook for 2-3 minutes, until the sauce has thickened slightly.",
    "Stir in the chopped cilantro, salt, and pepper.",
    "Serve the Fluffy Crunchy Thai Corn Flour Pad hot, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
